mysql> select Track.Name as Track, Title as Album, Artist.Name as Artist FROM Track
    -> INNER JOIN Album on Track.AlbumId = Album.AlbumId
    -> INNER JOIN Artist on Album.ArtistId = Artist.ArtistId
    -> WHERE Artist.Name = 'U2';

mysql> select Track.Name as Track, Title as Album, Artist.Name as Artist FROM Track INNER JOIN Album on Track.AlbumId = Album.AlbumId INNER JOIN Artist on Album.ArtistId = Artist.ArtistId WHERE Artist.Name = 'U2' AND Track.Name = 'Pride (In The Name Of Love)';
+-----------------------------+-----------------------+--------+
| Track                       | Album                 | Artist |
+-----------------------------+-----------------------+--------+
| Pride (In The Name Of Love) | Rattle And Hum        | U2     |
| Pride (In The Name Of Love) | The Best Of 1980-1990 | U2     |
+-----------------------------+-----------------------+--------+
2 rows in set (0.00 sec)
